great sunshine beauty,'' Scavullo said.
   Ms. Alexis of ABC's ``Good Morning America'' has been ``my
favorite cover girl for years and I'm glad to see her on television
as a fashion editor.''
   Ms. Burke, of CBS' ``Designing Women,'' frets about her weight,
he said. ``Two things she'll never have trouble with are her lovely
skin and eyes.''
   Scavullo first photographed Ms. Rashad, of NBC's ``The Cosby
Show,'' with her baby for Harper's Bazaar. ``She was quite
fabulous,'' he said.
   Diane Sawyer, of CBS' ``60 Minutes,'' ``is a great beauty and a
marvelous newscaster with an incredibly personal style,'' Scavullo
said.
   And Ms. Cox, who appears in NBC's ``Family Ties,'' caught
Scavullo's eye while dancing with Bruce Springsteen in a music
video. ``I don't know if she's Irish, but she has gorgeous Irish
eyes,'' Scavullo said.
