<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WKD--Holbein Adv22-24   07-11 0718</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-WKD--Holbein, Adv 22-24,0733</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv22</NOTE>
